author: Ditte Rares
title: Ditte Rares
text: I order a Bugaboo Donkey Twin which was cheaper than in my home country and signed up for the 10% discount offered if you can wait 2-5 weeks for your order. However, I received the order only 5 days later and everything was in mint condition. Will and have recommended to others.
